<h1>Admin Panel</h1>
<p>Welcome to the admin panel. This will be expanded upon to be much more comprehensive, however, below you will find some useful optoins including; the ability to assign yourself to more clients, remove yourself from clients and import a new CSV file</p>

<h3>Manage your clients</h3>
<%= link_to 'Update clients >', profile_path(current_user), class: 'btn btn-default' %>

<h3>Upload New Data</h3>
<p>Accepts .csv files only.</p>
<%= form_tag('/projects/import/', multipart: true) do %>
  <%= file_field_tag :file %> <%= submit_tag 'Upload', class: 'btn btn-default', style: 'margin-top: 15px;' %>
<% end %>

<% simple_form_for(:user, :url => user_invitation_path) do |f| %>
    <%= f.error_notification %>
    
<div class="form-inputs">
    <%= f.input :email %>
</div>

<div class="form-actions">
    <%= f.button :submit %>
</div>
<% end %>